{"tid":901696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典傳媒稱台灣為「國家」 中共大使館抗議","createTime":"2018-11-14T08:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T09:45:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f923b5b869100fbb6eec6708db7d8dd03761c933","tid":901696,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"據中共駐瑞典大使館網站消息，近日，瑞典「新韋姆蘭報」刊登涉台文章，公然稱台灣為「國家」、中國大陸在國際上「孤立」台灣，號召支援「在台灣的自由的中國」。<br />\n<br />\n中共駐瑞典大使館嚴正指出，文章有關內容嚴重違背瑞典外交基本原則和國際關係基本準則，嚴重侵犯中國主權和領土完整。中共駐瑞典大使館已致信「新韋姆蘭報」表示堅決反對，並闡明中方立場如下：<br />\n<br />\n「世界上只有一個中國，中華人民共和國是代表全中國的唯一合法政府，台灣是中國領土不可分割的一部分，這早已為國際社會所公認。所有涉台問題必須按照一個中國原則處理，這是包括瑞典在內的國際社會的普遍共識，並由1971年聯大第2758號決議確認，也是人心所向，大勢所趨，勢不可擋。」<br />\n<br />\n中方還說，台灣問題事關中國主權、領土完整等核心利益，對中瑞關係健康穩定發展至關重要。「新韋姆蘭報」發表支持台獨的文章，嚴重誤導瑞典讀者，對中瑞友好造成負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n中共駐瑞典大使館希望「新韋姆蘭報」明辨是非，恪守一個中國原則，尊重中國主權和領土完整，立即糾正錯誤，不要逆潮流而動，避免再出現任何有違一個中國原則的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3480192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3480192&d=wYIrc0MOATNyAI01%2F0rN1AtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=c4883d47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3480192</a>"},{"pid":"26c12fc252136410dba84a93589f97d3fcaa736f","tid":901696,"uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IW7UCGOIFWok3WzGAt7TZQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/0ccb6a921b3c879e5cbe8949b55d5ff1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIW7UCGOIFWok3WzGAt7TZQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F0ccb6a921b3c879e5cbe8949b55d5ff1&h=0197e182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0e674f0434cc3261f1f4f41808cb0826e40d3de","tid":901696,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"中華民就是台灣,台灣即係中華民國"},{"pid":"dcd4d6722a2f955762e4b9a54d21a463b2da8e2b","tid":901696,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6131d6f0b30343e4e24d9533dd78db27db55d4c3","tid":901696,"uid":42283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"除左港澳根本冇人怕你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ea396552734c7ba544445c24fe1eef37eb4997","tid":901696,"uid":58116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74480919836e27409f30b71f4ea4cc4505b1808","tid":901696,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"絕對認同世界上只有一個中國<br />\n同埋一個香港仲有一個台灣<br />\n3個地方黎唔好成日認親認戚"}]}